description: The CI International Quality Dividend Growth Index ETF seeks to track the price and yield performance of the WisdomTree International Quality Dividend Growth Index CAD (the "Index"), a fundamentally weighted Index designed to provide exposure to dividend paying companies in the developed world (excluding Canada and the U.S.) with growth characteristics. The Index is comprised of the 300 companies in the WisdomTree International Equity Index with market capitalization of at least US$1 billion, with the best combined rank of growth and quality factors.
name: CI International Quality Dividend Growth Index ETF
